        "accordion_whats-included": "<p>This isn’t a coat-it-and-hope mask. It works <em>inside</em> the strand — hydrolysed keratin, collagen and Acetyl Hexapeptide-8 fill the gaps in damaged hair and seal in moisture.</p><ul><li><strong>It repairs — it doesn’t just straighten.</strong> Restores your hair’s health without changing your natural texture.</li><li><strong>No formaldehyde, no flat-iron, no salon.</strong> A 5–20 minute rinse-out mask, gentle on coloured and over-processed hair.</li><li><strong>20 single-use treatments per box</strong> — backed by a 30-day money-back guarantee.</li></ul>",
        "accordion_how-it-works": "<ul><li><strong>Less breakage, fuller-looking hair.</strong> When strands stop snapping mid-length, hair looks thicker and healthier from root to tip.</li><li><strong>Frizz tamed, shine restored.</strong> A smooth, glass-like finish from the very first treatment.</li><li><strong>Hydration that lasts.</strong> Dry, brittle, lifeless hair brought back to life — and the results build for weeks.</li></ul>",
